column2: graph = ggplot(fp.threeItem, aes(x=fp.threeItem$Month_num, y = fp.threeItem$Data_value, fill = Item)) + geom_bar(stat = "identity") + labs(x = "Month", y = "Price of Item") + scale_x_continuous(breaks=1:12,labels=c(unique(fp.threeItem$Month)))+theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1))
